        "subject": "=Action needed: Outstanding invoice for {{ $json.company }}",
        "message": "=<p>Hey {{ $json.first_name }},</p><p>I wanted to follow up on the outstanding invoice for the {{ $json.company }} project. It's been {{ $json.days_since_invoice }} days since the invoice was sent.</p><p>I understand things can slip through the cracks \u2014 could you let me know the status of the payment? If there are any issues, I'm happy to work with you to resolve them.</p><p>Cheers,<br>Anthony<br>Veteran Vectors</p>",
        "options": {
